sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UI as machine-ui
    participant BC as BuyController
    participant Inv as InventoryService
    participant Om as OmisePaymentService
    participant DB as MySQL

    UI->>BC: POST /api/buy/create-draft (cart, coupon, machine)
    BC->>Inv: check_stock, _resolve_pricing
    BC->>Inv: create_pending_order(charge_id=draft_*)
    Inv->>DB: INSERT orders + items
    BC-->>UI: charge_id = draft_...

    Note over UI: ลูกค้าแตะบัตร / เลือกชำระ

    UI->>BC: POST /api/buy/checkout (draft_id, payment_id, ...)
    BC->>Inv: get_order_totals_by_charge_id(draft_id)
    BC->>Om: create_charge
    BC->>Inv: upgrade_draft_order(draft_id → charge.id)
    Inv->>DB: UPDATE orders SET charge_id, ...
    BC->>BC: clear in-memory draft keys
    BC-->>UI: pending_payment or paid
